The paper deals with active object tracking, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The proposed system involves multiple cameras collaborating with each other, which falls under the category of multi-modal systems (cs.MM) and distributed systems (cs.SY). The system also involves controllers and decision-making, which are key components of artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
